OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining showers should quickly fade
OL,7,Fto leave a dry and settled night with
OL,8,Fprolonged clear spells and light
OL,9,Fwinds. Cloud increasing a little later
OL,10,Fin the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA dry start to the morning but
OL,13,Fcloudy thickening with rain to follow.
OL,14,FRemaining rather grey and wet during
OL,15,Fthe afternoon with heavy outbreaks of
OL,16,Frain possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
